txt.en: Search interiors within after-battle Osgiliath for enemies and hidden supplies.
You should talk to Mablung, who can be found at the Ranger encampment in after-battle Osgiliath.
'Good, you found some supplies and saw that the buildings were clear of enemies. These goods will be most useful for us in the days and weeks ahead.'
Mablung has asked you to search Osgiliath's ruined buildings for enemies and hidden supplies.

'Many of the buildings in Osgiliath are no longer standing or are partially collapsed from the conflict here. I would like you to search the few remaining structures for any supplies you might find. The Easterlings or Haradrim may have stashed supplies in these buildings before they marched on the Pelennor. I hope that no foes remain in these buildings.'
